-- CNP Assurances sells to Barclays its stake in BVP for $555 mln
-- By Natalie Huet
-- Mon Dec 22, 2014 11:55AM EST
-- None



PARIS, Dec 22 (Reuters) - CNP Assurances <CNPP.PA> said on Monday it was selling to Barclays Bank <BARC.L> its 50 percent stake in CNP Barclays Vida Y Pensiones (CNP BVP), for 453 million euros ($555 million) including a special dividend.

